data.description: Newly updated, this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home comes with a 13 year tax abatement! The home features 2 Master Suites and a 3rd, very private bedroom. The first Master Suite is on the first floor with a modern, in-suite full-bathroom and walk in closet. The other Master Suite is on the second floor with it's own, in-suite, full bath and walk in closet. A loft off the upstairs Master Suite, overlooks the kitchen providing a dramatic view from both upstairs and downstairs. The loft is perfect for a home office or sitting area. The kitchen has new, black onyx appliances with leather, quartz counter-tops. Character hickory, hardwood flooring can be seen throughout the first floor. From the kitchen, you'll see two staircases with rod iron spindles. The second staircase leads to the third, private bedroom. Throughout the house, all hardware and fixtures are upgraded. "Soft-close" cabinets and drawers are throughout the house as well. Outside, the modern front entry and siding has beautiful street appeal. A privacy fence incorporates a quaint patio for entertaining. From the private, gated yard, you can access the single garage. Dramatic, vaulted ceilings throughout. This is a must see home located in the growing and popular, Ohio City community. This well designed, open concept home will not last long. Call 440-503-5200 now for your private showing.
data.whatILove: Modern with a tax abatement for 13 more years! Easy access to the highways and downtown! Walkable to many hot spots and a lot of new building activity.
